# ─── long-distance scene cards (17 entries) ───
# All use placeholder art until PNGs are generated.
# Tags carry semantic markers for engine TRs not yet implemented:
#   draggable_false  → card cannot be dragged (TR-LD-1)
#   chase:<target>   → card has ChaseBehavior toward target (TR-LD-2)
#   visual:<tag>     → custom CardVisual tag (TR-LD-3, e.g. rabbit_jump_fast)
#   carry_forward    → persists into subsequent scenes (TR-LD-4)

